<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Joseph </PERSON> <PERSON> B. </PERSON> <PERSON> Frazier </PERSON> has covered <LOCATION> Central </LOCATION> <LOCATION> America </LOCATION> and its affairs for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> since 1979.
