<HEAD>Jetliner Narrowly Misses Light Plane Near Cleveland Airport</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: New thruout without FAA confirmation, quotes from flight
attendant</NOTE>
<DATELINE>CLEVELAND (AP) </DATELINE>
