<HEAD>General Strike Shuts Down City At Center Of Ethnic Dispute</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: LEADS with 12 grafs to UPDATE with demonstrations continue in
Yerevan; details, giving different figures on number of protesters.
PICKS up 11th pvs, Armenians began .... Edits to TRIM. Gives
